00:12:49.630 --> 00:12:51.640 align:middle line:90%
I go, what's the relevance?

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:54.320 align:middle line:84%
Well, first, you have to
have an operating system.

00:12:54.320 --> 00:12:55.480 align:middle line:90%
I say, oh.

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:58.480 align:middle line:84%
