up, operating system is there.

00:13:09.770 --> 00:13:10.950 align:middle line:90%
Boots up.

00:13:10.950 --> 00:13:11.950 align:middle line:90%
Now, I say do something.

00:13:11.950 --> 00:13:12.867 align:middle line:90%
And you go, like what?

00:13:12.867 --> 00:13:15.890 align:middle line:10%
I say, oh, a drawing,
spreadsheet, Word document.

00:13:15.890 --> 00:13:17.690 align:middle line:10%
I go, oh, I can't do that.

00:13:17.690 --> 00:13:19.040 align:middle line:10%
I say, why not?

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:21.240 align:middle line:10%
First, you have to
put in a program

00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:23.210 align:middle line:10%
so you can operate the computer.

00:13:23.210 --> 00:13:27.680 align:middle line:10%
The startup, booting up, it
