is not at a higher vibration

00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:41.690 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness, alpha
and beta and gamma.

00:13:41.690 --> 00:13:44.240 align:middle line:90%
It's at a lower vibration.

00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:46.310 align:middle line:10%
By testing with
wires on a head--

00:13:46.310 --> 00:13:49.700 align:middle line:10%
EEG-- the vibration
of a developing child

00:13:49.700 --> 00:13:53.747 align:middle line:10%
is predominantly in theta,
which is below consciousness.

00:13:53.747 --> 00:13:54.830 align:middle line:10%
What does theta represent?

00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:59.690 align:middle line:10%
I said, it's expressed
as, well, a child's

00:13:59.690 --> 00:14:02.120 align:middle line:10%
creating a reality,
a fantasy world,

00:14:02.120 --> 00:14:03.650 align:middle line:10%
coming into the real world.

00:14:03.650 --> 00:14:06.810 align:middle line:10%
Theta is a mixture of
fantasy and reality.

00:14:06.810 --> 00:14:11.600 align:middle line:10%
I can ride a broom, but in my
mind as a kid, it's not a broom.

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:14.780 align:middle line:90%
It is a full-blown stallion.

00:14:14.780 --> 00:14:18.403 align:middle line:10%
And so my mother says, give me
the broom, I'm looking at her,

00:14:18.403 --> 00:14:20.570 align:middle line:10%
I don't even know what the
heck she's talking about.

00:14:20.570 --> 00:14:22.250 align:middle line:10%
This isn't a broom,
it's a horse.

00:14:22.250 --> 00:14:25.520 align:middle line:10%
Or I love it, the
famous tea party.

00:14:25.520 --> 00:14:28.890 align:middle line:84%
We pour nothing into that
cup and drink this nothing

00:14:28.890 --> 00:14:31.620 align:middle line:84%
