the best tea I ever had.

00:14:31.620 --> 00:14:34.230 align:middle line:90%
And I go, theta--

00:14:34.230 --> 00:14:36.930 align:middle line:84%
fantasy and reality
coming together.

00:14:36.930 --> 00:14:40.470 align:middle line:84%
That's a character-- up
until, by seven, it changes,

00:14:40.470 --> 00:14:43.890 align:middle line:84%
because then, we get a higher
vibration called consciousness,

00:14:43.890 --> 00:14:44.890 align:middle line:90%
alpha.

00:14:44.890 --> 00:14:48.780 align:middle line:84%
So in this pre-seven
period, I say, what is

00:14:48.780 --> 00:14:50.430 align:middle line:90%
