00:15:22.270 --> 00:15:24.810 align:middle line:10%
I say, so what is hypnosis?

00:15:24.810 --> 00:15:27.600 align:middle line:84%
It takes environmental
experiences

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:30.940 align:middle line:84%
