do what you want.

00:15:43.150 --> 00:15:44.850 align:middle line:10%
And so where do you
get the rules from?

00:15:44.850 --> 00:15:47.430 align:middle line:10%
A young kid doesn't read a book.

00:15:47.430 --> 00:15:49.500 align:middle line:10%
I say, ah, nature
helped him out.

00:15:49.500 --> 00:15:51.180 align:middle line:84%
Said, you want to
know the rules,

00:15:51.180 --> 00:15:53.790 align:middle line:84%
put you in record,
watch your parents.

00:15:53.790 --> 00:15:54.990 align:middle line:90%
Watch your siblings.

00:15:54.990 --> 00:15:56.340 align:middle line:90%
Watch your community.

00:15:56.340 --> 00:15:59.610 align:middle line:10%
What you're observing is not
going into the conscious mind.

00:15:59.610 --> 00:16:01.320 align:middle line:10%
It's not functioning
at that level.

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:03.930 align:middle line:10%
What you're observing is
going download straight

00:16:03.930 --> 00:16:05.590 align:middle line:10%
