No, it's not working.

00:16:28.860 --> 00:16:29.970 align:middle line:90%
I say, why is it relevant?

00:16:29.970 --> 00:16:31.200 align:middle line:10%
And the answer is this.

00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:34.980 align:middle line:10%
What got downloaded into
your subconscious programming

00:16:34.980 --> 00:16:37.830 align:middle line:10%
