00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:39.075 align:middle line:10%
It wasn't filtered by you.

00:16:39.075 --> 00:16:40.200 align:middle line:10%
I say, what does that mean?

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:43.410 align:middle line:10%
I say, I can get good
