self-sabotaging, limiting

00:16:57.330 --> 00:16:58.680 align:middle line:10%
beliefs that we acquire.

00:16:58.680 --> 00:17:02.550 align:middle line:10%
So I say, oh, I'm getting
programmed, and most of them

00:17:02.550 --> 00:17:07.020 align:middle line:10%
