00:18:26.260 --> 00:18:28.720 align:middle line:10%
I go, well, then, you
manifest Heaven on Earth.

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:31.962 align:middle line:84%
And then I go, well, this
is really good, because I

00:18:31.962 --> 00:18:32.920 align:middle line:90%
