00:18:32.920 --> 00:18:38.120 align:middle line:84%
I go, one small monkey wrench
that blows the whole thing.

00:18:38.120 --> 00:18:40.140 align:middle line:90%
And I go, what is that?

00:18:40.140 --> 00:18:41.850 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness is
indeed creative,

00:18:41.850 --> 00:18:44.100 align:middle line:90%
but consciousness can think.

00:18:44.100 --> 00:18:47.010 align:middle line:84%
And being creative, that
thinking, is really good.

00:18:47.010 --> 00:18:50.820 align:middle line:84%
But then I say, if
consciousness is thinking, then

00:18:50.820 --> 00:18:55.930 align:middle line:84%
