I'm seeking going to come from?

00:18:55.930 --> 00:18:58.560 align:middle line:10%
It's going to come
from my brain.

00:18:58.560 --> 00:19:00.630 align:middle line:10%
Consciousness is
reviewing, thinking,

00:19:00.630 --> 00:19:02.350 align:middle line:10%
