Who's driving the car?

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:48.840 align:middle line:84%
And this is the
crux of the problem.

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:54.290 align:middle line:84%
The moment consciousness is
busy, subconscious is autopilot.

00:19:54.290 --> 00:19:55.550 align:middle line:90%
It knows how to walk.

00:19:55.550 --> 00:19:57.080 align:middle line:90%
It knows anything you learn.

00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:58.040 align:middle line:90%
You drive the car.

