You learned how
to drive the car.

00:19:59.810 --> 00:20:00.920 align:middle line:90%
Your job.

00:20:00.920 --> 00:20:03.660 align:middle line:84%
Once you learn it, you don't
have to think about it.

00:20:03.660 --> 00:20:05.240 align:middle line:90%
It's an automatic habit.

00:20:05.240 --> 00:20:07.960 align:middle line:90%
So basically, it says this.

00:20:07.960 --> 00:20:10.900 align:middle line:84%
You can create your life
with your conscious mind,

00:20:10.900 --> 00:20:18.445 align:middle line:84%
