00:20:18.445 --> 00:20:19.570 align:middle line:90%
Oh, so what does that mean?

00:20:19.570 --> 00:20:23.590 align:middle line:10%
I say, the 95% of the
day, your behavior

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:27.700 align:middle line:10%
is not controlled by the
creative wishes and desires.

00:20:27.700 --> 00:20:30.040 align:middle line:10%
It's now controlled by
