And I go, what if those
are negative programs--

00:20:33.790 --> 00:20:35.470 align:middle line:10%
which 70% are?

00:20:35.470 --> 00:20:38.350 align:middle line:90%
I say, this is the problem.

00:20:38.350 --> 00:20:40.870 align:middle line:84%
Since consciousness is
not observing my behavior

00:20:40.870 --> 00:20:44.500 align:middle line:84%
because it's inside
looking for thoughts, then

00:20:44.500 --> 00:20:47.140 align:middle line:84%
whatever behavior is being
expressed at that moment,

00:20:47.140 --> 00:20:49.690 align:middle line:84%
consciousness does
not observe it.

00:20:49.690 --> 00:20:51.160 align:middle line:90%
It's inside.

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:52.660 align:middle line:10%
So I say, well,
what does that mean?

00:20:52.660 --> 00:20:55.600 align:middle line:10%
I say, well, if you
have a negative program,

00:20:55.600 --> 00:21:00.140 align:middle line:10%
you will manifest negative
behavior and you won't see it.

00:21:00.140 --> 00:21:01.580 align:middle line:90%
Everybody else will.

00:21:01.580 --> 00:21:03.760 align:middle line:90%
So how many years now?

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:08.160 align:middle line:10%
30 some plus years I've
used this one story.

00:21:08.160 --> 00:21:11.120 align:middle line:10%
It's been repeated 1,000 times.

00:21:11.120 --> 00:21:13.880 align:middle line:84%
But it's so pivotal
to understanding

00:21:13.880 --> 00:21:15.500 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to say it again.

00:21:15.500 --> 00:21:17.480 align:middle line:10%
And that is this.

00:21:17.480 --> 00:21:20.330 align:middle line:10%
You have a friend, and you
know your friend's behavior

00:21:20.330 --> 00:21:21.650 align:middle line:10%
very well.

00:21:21.650 --> 00:21:25.010 align:middle line:10%
And you happen to know
your friend's parent.

00:21:25.010 --> 00:21:28.650 align:middle line:10%
And one day, you see your friend
has the exact same behavior

00:21:28.650 --> 00:21:29.450 align:middle line:10%
as their parent.

00:21:29.450 --> 00:21:32.480 align:middle line:10%
Well, of course,
you can't hold back.

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:35.850 align:middle line:10%
Hey, Bill, you're
just like your dad.

00:21:35.850 --> 00:21:38.120 align:middle line:10%
Then I say, back away from
Bill, because the moment

00:21:38.120 --> 00:21:40.400 align:middle line:10%
