00:23:39.100 --> 00:23:40.530 align:middle line:10%
So it's not me.

00:23:40.530 --> 00:23:45.660 align:middle line:84%
The universe is
not supporting me.

00:23:45.660 --> 00:23:47.700 align:middle line:10%
