And I got this crap instead.

00:23:55.410 --> 00:23:57.300 align:middle line:10%
I'm a victim.

00:23:57.300 --> 00:24:01.470 align:middle line:84%
I go, again, definition
of victim-- powerless.

00:24:01.470 --> 00:24:03.540 align:middle line:10%
It says, I have great
wishes and desires

00:24:03.540 --> 00:24:06.760 align:middle line:10%
