01:12:03.940 --> 01:12:06.540 align:middle line:84%
But, well, you can
make a bigger one.

01:12:06.540 --> 01:12:07.340 align:middle line:90%
What?

01:12:07.340 --> 01:12:10.220 align:middle line:10%
A dinosaur-- 50-foot
instead of 5-inch.

01:12:10.220 --> 01:12:11.360 align:middle line:10%
I say, guess what?

01:12:11.360 --> 01:12:15.320 align:middle line:84%
Take the blueprint
