01:12:46.970 --> 01:12:47.770 align:middle line:90%
Why?

01:12:47.770 --> 01:12:51.230 align:middle line:84%
Because a lizard is the
prototype of a 50-foot dinosaur.

01:12:51.230 --> 01:12:53.570 align:middle line:10%
And I say, where does
that relate to in humans?

01:12:53.570 --> 01:12:59.990 align:middle line:10%
I go, industrial civilization
is the mechanized version

01:12:59.990 --> 01:13:02.660 align:middle line:10%
of human civilization.

01:13:02.660 --> 01:13:04.780 align:middle line:84%
And it started out as
small little things.

01:13:04.780 --> 01:13:05.580 align:middle line:90%
As what?

01:13:05.580 --> 01:13:07.770 align:middle line:90%
Mom and pop shops.

01:13:07.770 --> 01:13:08.640 align:middle line:90%
But then, what?

01:13:08.640 --> 01:13:13.120 align:middle line:84%
As they became successful,
they grew bigger and bigger.

01:13:13.120 --> 01:13:15.870 align:middle line:84%
And they became
dinosaurs of industry.

01:13:15.870 --> 01:13:17.760 align:middle line:84%
And I go, there's
